algorithms.graphs

Class HierholzersEulerCircuit

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.graphs.HierholzersEulerCircuit

  • public class HierholzersEulerCircuit
extends java.lang.Object
    Hierholzer’s Algorithm to create a euler circuit from a directed graph. Euler circuit is a path that traverses every edge of a graph, and the path ends on the starting vertex. 
     The implementation follows from:
 https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/hierholzers-algorithm-directed-graph/
 written by
 https://in.linkedin.com/in/ashutosh-kumar-9527a7105
